WEBVTT

00:10:59.559 --> 00:11:01.039
or water wings.

00:11:01.063 --> 00:11:07.030
The mystery of grace is that God loves
Henry Kissinger and Vladimir Putin

00:11:07.054 --> 00:11:08.213
and me

00:11:08.237 --> 00:11:12.593
exactly as much as He or She
loves your new grandchild.

00:11:12.988 --> 00:11:14.205
Go figure.

00:11:14.229 --> 00:11:16.006
(Laughter)

00:11:16.030 --> 00:11:19.367
The movement of grace
is what changes us, heals us

00:11:19.391 --> 00:11:21.389
and heals our world.

00:11:21.413 --> 00:11:25.184
To summon grace, say, "Help,"
and then buckle up.

00:11:25.208 --> 00:11:27.898
Grace finds you exactly where you are,

00:11:27.922 --> 00:11:30.447
but it doesn't leave you
where it found you.